ActForeign Missions and International Organizations Act
SubjectArctic Council Ministerial Meeting 2015 — Privileges and Immunities Order
PrecisARCTIC COUNCIL MINISTERIAL MEETING 2015 - PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES ORDER in order to (1) grant limited privileges to foreign State representatives not otherwise protected under customary international law during their attendance at the 2015 Arctic Council Ministerial Meeting in Iqaluit, Nunavut on April 24-25, 2015; and (2) grant the Royal Canadian Mounted Police primary responsibility to ensure the security for the proper functioning of the international meeting through the operation of s. 10.1 of the Foreign Mission and International Organizational Act.
